{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"configurationURL:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which it is added.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"identifier"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source’s contents and other metadata."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"configurationURL"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An initialized raster tile source."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize"},{"type":"text","text":" documentation for more information about tile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNRasterTileSource(im)initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","te